snippet.title: GlitchSPANKR Demo Trailer - Demo out now!
snippet.description:
Try the demo NOW on Steam!
https://bit.ly/GlitchSPANKR_YT

As a 12 year old gamer in the 90's, your curiosity was ignited when your Mom brought home a new game you weren't allowed to play. Big Booty Slapper 6. Unfortunately, there seems to be a rogue virus eating and corrupting your precious game! Using the GlitchSPANKR Antivirus software, dive into virtual worlds and Spank that Glitch! Or befriend him.
